column1: It makes it even more important to elect @JoeBiden @KamalaHarris and a Democratic Congress so we will be in a position to fix the damage the Supreme Court will do to health insurance coverage in the middle of the COVID-19 pandemic.

After we get COVID under control we must address the child care crisis. All families should be able to afford to send their kids to quality child care. Glad to see @JoeBiden include my bill to cap child care expenses at 7% for hardworking families in his #BuildBackBetter plan!

Thank you to all of our frontline workers who are helping our community through the #COVIDー19 pandemic. You are the backbone of our community. We will get through this crisis together and come out stronger and more united than ever. #SOULSaturday https://t.co/he5MqLc8jv

Looking forward to joining Filipinos for @JoeBiden today @ 3pm for a virtual conference on how the #COVID19 pandemic is impacting Filipinos in the US. Register here: https://t.co/nGXPDjdafB @TeamJoe https://t.co/x1dbh1K004

Honored to officially be declared the 2020 Democratic nominee for the 3rd congressional district of Virginia! While I am grateful my primary focus at this time is helping our community address the Coronavirus. That’s why I’m back in DC working to pass additional economic relief.
